Title: Display the user and version in the user and help menu
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1605611605
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0i2

Old Checkmk versions displayed the user in the top right and
the version in the top left of the window. Now the user and
version are displayed at the beggining of the user and help
menu, respectively.

The global setting "Show Checkmk edition & version in the
sidebar" is removed.
